commit.message:
libaudit: add ausearch_cur_event (#357)

* libaudit: add ausearch_cur_event

The ausearch_cur_event function will scan the current event of the input source
and evaluate whether any record in an event contains the data being searched for.

* ausearch_cur_event: do not reposition cursor when no match was found
